  m_Name: TakasuTaiga
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CharacterInfo
  characterName: Takasu Taiga
  description: The breadwinner and matriarch of the family. With her strong fighting
    spirit and charisma, she became a feisty and wealthy salarywoman to support her
    family of six, but being a mother has been an absolute nightmare. The fear of
    where her daughters will be in the future is constantly looming over her, and
    she feels totally powerless over them, especially with how much bigger they were
    compared to her. Well, as long as everyone comes home at the end of the day,
    they'll be fine, right?
